          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">VNTR</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Locus-3</ENAMEX> locus contained a single repeat in the three
          
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">B. melitensis</ENAMEX> biovars.
