          As mentioned above, <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">VNTR</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Locus-4</ENAMEX> of the 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">B. suis</ENAMEX> biovar <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX> sequenced genome
