          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">B. ovis</ENAMEX> , and 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">B. suis</ENAMEX> biovars <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">2, 4 and 5</TIMEX>, were
