          allelic ladder exhibited by the 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">B. melitensis</ENAMEX> or 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">B. abortus biovars</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fig</ENAMEX>. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX>, starred
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">alleles</ENAMEX>).
          There was disagreement between the fragment sizes
          calculated from the published genomic sequences and the
