          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">upstream</ENAMEX> and downstream of each of the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">eight</NUMEX>,
          hypervariable, repeat loci. Minimizing the sizes of the
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">amplicons</ENAMEX> made the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">8</NUMEX>-bp size increments visually distinct
          on agarose gels (<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fig</ENAMEX>. 3A) and clearly resolved by
